sec.title: Competing interests
sec.p: Drs. Heilbron, Fontanillas, Alipanahi, Cannon, and members of the 23andMe Research Team are employees of and have stock, stock options, or both, in 23andMe. Dr. Nalls is supported by a consulting contract between Data Tecnica International and the National Institute on Aging (project number: Z01-AG000949-02). The remaining authors declare no competing interests.
